versity uk she worked at lecg an economic and financial consulting firm and at the uk treasury in london where she worked on policies to manage investment bank failures she is interested in sustainable development and energy and resource issues given their importance to inclusive growth prospects in countries like india search people everything support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
